{"id":84,"category_slug":"short-stories","category_name":"Short Stories","position":54,"title":"54. Differences","subtitle":"","level":"A1","parts":23,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/short-stories/54-differences.84/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/0-54-differences.mp3","transcript":"Are you tall or short?\nAre you big or small?\nPeople come in many different shapes and sizes.\nSome people wear size small clothes.\nOther people wear size medium clothes.\nThere are people who wear large size clothes.\nSome people even wear extra large clothes.\nSome people are thin. Some people are fat.\nSome people are in between.\nThere are people with short hair.\nOther people have long hair.\nSome people have no hair at all.\nNo two people are exactly alike.\nSome people have long legs.\nI have short legs.\nI don't walk as fast as a person with long legs.\nI am not a tall person. In fact, I am quite short.\nMy feet are a size seven.\nMy mother has size five feet.\nMy father has size twelve feet.\nWe are all different sizes.\nIt is not a bad thing.\nIt is a good thing that we are all unique.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:55:49","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Are you tall or short?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/1.mp3","time_start":2.4,"time_end":4.26},{"position":2,"content":"Are you big or small?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/2.mp3","time_start":4.26,"time_end":5.7},{"position":3,"content":"People come in many different shapes and sizes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/3.mp3","time_start":5.8,"time_end":8.59},{"position":4,"content":"Some people wear size small clothes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/4.mp3","time_start":8.6,"time_end":10.86},{"position":5,"content":"Other people wear size medium clothes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/5.mp3","time_start":10.77,"time_end":13.35},{"position":6,"content":"There are people who wear large size clothes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/6.mp3","time_start":13.49,"time_end":16.0},{"position":7,"content":"Some people even wear extra large clothes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/7.mp3","time_start":16.0,"time_end":18.8},{"position":8,"content":"Some people are thin. Some people are fat.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/8.mp3","time_start":19.3,"time_end":22.3},{"position":9,"content":"Some people are in between.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/9.mp3","time_start":22.3,"time_end":24.3},{"position":10,"content":"There are people with short hair.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/10-2019-05-09-09-11-18.mp3","time_start":24.7,"time_end":26.36},{"position":11,"content":"Other people have long hair.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/11.mp3","time_start":26.34,"time_end":28.0},{"position":12,"content":"Some people have no hair at all.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/12.mp3","time_start":28.0,"time_end":30.0},{"position":13,"content":"No two people are exactly alike.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/13.mp3","time_start":30.4,"time_end":33.0},{"position":14,"content":"Some people have long legs.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/14.mp3","time_start":33.0,"time_end":34.68},{"position":15,"content":"I have short legs.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/15.mp3","time_start":34.68,"time_end":35.96},{"position":16,"content":"I don't walk as fast as a person with long legs.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/16.mp3","time_start":36.0,"time_end":38.6},{"position":17,"content":"I am not a tall person. In fact, I am quite short.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/17.mp3","time_start":39.0,"time_end":42.8},{"position":18,"content":"My feet are a size seven.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/18.mp3","time_start":43.0,"time_end":45.04},{"position":19,"content":"My mother has size five feet.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/19.mp3","time_start":45.04,"time_end":47.04},{"position":20,"content":"My father has size twelve feet.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/20.mp3","time_start":47.04,"time_end":49.2},{"position":21,"content":"We are all different sizes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/21.mp3","time_start":49.4,"time_end":51.26},{"position":22,"content":"It is not a bad thing.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/22.mp3","time_start":51.4,"time_end":52.86},{"position":23,"content":"It is a good thing that we are all unique.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/54-differences-2019-03-29-10-22-58/23.mp3","time_start":52.86,"time_end":55.5}]}